This is the readme for the Phing tasks needed to build modules for Zibo.

Installing the tasks
--------------------
- copy or link the php files from the tasks directory to <phing-directory>/tasks/ext
  (eg. /usr/share/php/phing/tasks/ext)
- add the following lines to the task definition file (eg. /usr/share/php/data/phing/tasks/defaults.properties)

    modulenameproperty=phing.tasks.ext.ModuleNamePropertyTask
    moduleversionproperty=phing.tasks.ext.ModuleVersionPropertyTask
    
That's it, happy building!

PS: Don't forget your php settings (eg./etc/php5/cli/php.ini)
    
    phar.readonly = Off